{"tid":2059903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美神盾艦今巡弋台灣北部海域","createTime":"2020-06-11T09:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T15:16:26.000Z","uid":75969,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0e29536a6172b2c2e92e038cc2053ccf1ef480dd","tid":2059903,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:07:36.000Z","msg":"據了解，美軍勃克級神盾飛彈驅逐艦「佩拉爾塔號」（USS Rafael Peralta，DDG 115）於今(11)日出現在台灣北部東海海域，並向馬祖方向航行。後續航行目標未知。<br />\n<br />\n美國海軍「佩拉爾塔號」於2017年服役，是第64艘勃克級驅逐艦，其具備新一代「整體防空與飛彈防禦」（IAMD）能力，除了執行巡弋、危機反應、制海、火力投射等各項任務，還能同時與空中、水面與水下目標接戰。<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------<br />\n-------------------------------<br />\n---------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n此外，大陸遼寧海事局6月1日曾發布航行警告稱，6月2日至16日解放軍將在渤海執行軍事任務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200611002963-260409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20200611002963-260409&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRD2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=89d1bf7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200611002963-260409</a>"},{"pid":"25a79e71688349017aed449913a9a4f5f4bd8399","tid":2059903,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:15:30.000Z","msg":"散步嚇小支支？"},{"pid":"85c850f7748e53095bd04e8e114fd9fda8d7a7f1","tid":2059903,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0981bccf1fc2492331880bb317659fc97393fd","tid":2059903,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:16:23.000Z","msg":"堅決反對, 強烈遺責"},{"pid":"d376dde128b1c4fb61798be9ee678d033164258f","tid":2059903,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:24:20.000Z","msg":"支那：好嬲好